        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Is Leadpages good for beginners with no coding experience?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Absolutely. Leadpages was designed for non-technical users. The drag-and-drop editor, pre-built templates, and intuitive interface mean you can build and publish a professional landing page in under an hour — no coding, no developer, no frustration. If you can use PowerPoint, you can use Leadpages.",
