        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Yes. Leadpages includes built-in checkout pages powered by Stripe. You can sell digital products, services, and even physical goods directly from your landing pages without needing a separate e-commerce platform. Payment processing, order bumps, and checkout customization are all included on the Pro plan and above.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "How does Leadpages compare to building pages in WordPress?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "WordPress page builders like Elementor are powerful but often require more setup, plugin management, and hosting optimization. Leadpages handles hosting, speed, and security for you. The templates are conversion-optimized out of the box, and features like A/B testing and integrated analytics are built in — not bolted on through third-party plugins. For marketers focused on results rather than technical maintenance, Leadpages is typically the faster, cleaner path.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      }
